# Prompt Lengkap: Website Jasa Tugas

Berikut prompt siap pakai yang bisa kamu berikan ke AI coding assistant (Claude, ChatGPT, Cursor, dll):

---

## 📋 MASTER PROMPT

```
Buatkan website lengkap "Jasa Tugas" menggunakan stack berikut:
- Backend: Express.js (Node.js)
- Frontend: HTML + Tailwind CSS CDN (modern, rapi, menarik)
- Database: GitHub Repository sebagai penyimpanan JSON (read-write via GitHub API)
- Auth: Firebase Authentication (email/password, session 30 hari)
- Payment: Atlantic Payment Gateway

==================================================
🔐 AUTHENTICATION (Firebase Gratis)
==================================================
- Gunakan Firebase Auth dengan email & password
- Setelah login, simpan token ke cookie dengan maxAge 30 hari
- Middleware Express cek token Firebase di setiap route protected
- Halaman: /login dan /register
- Setelah login redirect ke /dashboard

==================================================
💾 DATABASE (GitHub Repository JSON)
==================================================
Gunakan GitHub REST API untuk baca-tulis file JSON:
- Endpoint: https://api.github.com/repos/{owner}/{repo}/contents/{path}
- Auth: GitHub Personal Access Token (PAT) via Authorization header
- Simpan data dalam file JSON di repo:
  - data/users.json → data user
  - data/orders.json → data pesanan tugas
  - data/services.json → daftar jasa/layanan

Fungsi helper yang wajib dibuat:
async function readGithubFile(path) - GET file, decode base64, return JSON
async function writeGithubFile(path, content, sha) - PUT file, encode base64, commit

Selalu fetch SHA terbaru sebelum write untuk menghindari conflict.

==================================================
🎨 TAMPILAN (Tailwind CSS)
==================================================
Tema: Gelap elegan dengan aksen biru/ungu
- Font: Inter dari Google Fonts
- Animasi halus (transition, hover effects)
- Fully responsive (mobile-first)
- Komponen: navbar, card layanan, badge status, modal, progress steps

Wajib ada di setiap halaman:
- Navbar: Logo "JasaTugas.id" + menu (Beranda, Layanan, Login/Dashboard)
- Footer: copyright, link sosmed
- Loading spinner saat fetch data
- Toast notification (success/error)

==================================================
📄 HALAMAN USER (Alur Utama)
==================================================

1. / → Landing Page
   - Hero section: headline besar + CTA "Pesan Sekarang"
   - Section: Cara Kerja (3 langkah dengan ikon)
   - Section: Daftar Layanan Jasa (card grid)
   - Section: Testimoni dummy
   - Section: FAQ

2. /layanan → Daftar Semua Jasa
   - Card tiap layanan: nama, deskripsi, harga, estimasi, tombol "Pesan"
   - Data layanan dari data/services.json
   - Filter/search layanan

3. /pesan/:serviceId → Form Pemesanan (protected, harus login)
   Step 1 - Detail Tugas:
   - Input: judul tugas, deskripsi lengkap
   - Upload file/foto (support jpg, png, pdf, docx, max 10MB)
   - File di-encode base64 dan simpan ke orders.json
   - Tombol "Lanjut ke Pembayaran"

   Step 2 - Pilih Metode Pembayaran:
   - Tampilkan metode dari Atlantic API: GET /deposit/metode
   - Tampilkan card: nama metode, logo, fee, min/max
   - Default pilih QRIS
   - Tombol "Buat Pembayaran"

   Step 3 - Halaman Pembayaran:
   - Panggil Atlantic API POST /deposit/create dengan:
     api_key, reff_id (orderId), nominal (harga layanan), type, metode
   - Tampilkan QR code image dari response (qr_image)
   - Tampilkan countdown timer expired_at
   - Polling status setiap 5 detik ke /api/check-payment/:orderId
   - Jika status "success" → redirect ke /dashboard dengan notif sukses

4. /dashboard → Dashboard User (protected)
   - Header: "Halo, {nama}!" + ringkasan statistik
   - Tabel/card daftar pesanan milik user
   - Kolom: No Urut, Layanan, Status (badge warna), Tanggal, Aksi
   - Status badge:
     🟡 "Menunggu Pembayaran" 
     🔵 "Antrean #X" 
     🟠 "Sedang Dikerjakan"
     🟢 "Selesai"
   - Jika status Selesai: tombol "Download File" muncul
   - Klik detail → modal tampilkan info lengkap pesanan

==================================================
🛠️ HALAMAN ADMIN
==================================================
URL: /admin/login
Kredensial hardcode: user=adm, pass=adm@123
Gunakan session express-session terpisah dari Firebase

5. /admin/dashboard → Overview admin
   - Statistik: total pesanan, pending, dikerjakan, selesai
   - Grafik sederhana (bar chart pakai Chart.js CDN)

6. /admin/pesanan → Manajemen Semua Pesanan
   - Tabel semua pesanan dari semua user
   - Filter: status, tanggal
   - Search: nama user, ID pesanan
   - Kolom: ID, User, Layanan, Status, Tanggal, Aksi

7. /admin/pesanan/:orderId → Detail & Kelola Pesanan
   Alur pengerjaan admin:
   
   Panel kiri: Info Pesanan
   - Detail user, layanan, deskripsi tugas
   - Preview file yang diupload user (tampilkan image/link download)
   
   Panel kanan: Update Status
   - Dropdown/tombol ubah status:
     ○ "Antrean #X" → otomatis isi nomor urut berdasarkan antrian
     ○ "Sedang Dikerjakan" 
     ○ "Selesai"
   - Upload File Hasil Pengerjaan:
     - Input upload file (jpg/png/pdf/docx)
     - Encode base64, simpan ke field "result_file" di orders.json
     - Tombol hanya aktif saat ubah status ke "Selesai"
   - Tombol "Simpan Perubahan"
   - Setelah simpan: redirect balik ke list pesanan

==================================================
🔌 API ROUTES (Express.js)
==================================================
POST /api/auth/register - register Firebase + simpan ke users.json
POST /api/auth/login - verifikasi Firebase token
GET  /api/services - ambil daftar layanan dari services.json
POST /api/orders - buat pesanan baru (simpan ke orders.json)
GET  /api/orders/my - pesanan milik user yang login
GET  /api/orders/:id - detail satu pesanan
POST /api/payment/create - panggil Atlantic deposit/create
GET  /api/payment/status/:orderId - cek status pembayaran (polling)
POST /api/admin/orders/:id/update - admin update status + upload file hasil

==================================================
💳 INTEGRASI ATLANTIC PAYMENT
==================================================
Gunakan axios untuk semua request ke Atlantic:

// Create deposit
POST https://atlantic-api-docs.vercel.app/deposit/create
Body (form-urlencoded):
  api_key: process.env.ATLANTIC_API_KEY
  reff_id: orderId (string unik)
  nominal: harga layanan (integer)
  type: "ewallet"
  metode: "qris" (atau pilihan user)

// Check status
POST https://atlantich2h.com/deposit/status  
Body:
  api_key: process.env.ATLANTIC_API_KEY
  id: atlantic_transaction_id (dari response create)

// Get metode
POST https://atlantich2h.com/deposit/metode
Body:
  api_key: process.env.ATLANTIC_API_KEY
  type: "ewallet"

Simpan atlantic_transaction_id ke orders.json saat buat pembayaran.
Saat polling, ambil atlantic_transaction_id dari orders.json lalu cek ke Atlantic.

